		<Description>A reusable hosted services for calling future methods asynchronously.</Description>
		<Copyright>2020-2021, Webefinity Pty Ltd</Copyright>
		<RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/hollandar/outrage-futures</RepositoryUrl>
